       "html": "<section class=\"wfx-wrap wfx-pad\" style=\"max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px 32px 28px\">\n  <div style=\"font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:#6b6557\">/ PORTFOLIO — 2019 → 2026</div>\n  <h1 class=\"wfx-h1\" style=\"font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:72px;line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin:14px 0 0\">THE WORK.</h1>\n  <p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;color:#3a352c;margin:18px 0 0;max-width:560px\">A decade of editorial covers, characters, brand systems and murals. Filter by what you need.</p>\n  <div class=\"wfx-chips\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;margin-top:30px\"><span class=\"wfx-chip\" data-filter=\"all\" style=\"cursor:pointer;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:9px 16px;border:2px solid #14110c;background:#14110c;color:#fff;box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #2b4cff\">ALL</span><span class=\"wfx-chip\" data-filter=\"Editorial\" style=\"cursor:pointer;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:9px 16px;border:2px solid #14110c;background:#fff;color:#14110c;box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #14110c\">EDITORIAL</span><span class=\"wfx-chip\" data-filter=\"Character\" style=\"cursor:pointer;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:9px 16px;border:2px solid #14110c;background:#fff;color:#14110c;box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #14110c\">CHARACTER</span><span class=\"wfx-chip\" data-filter=\"Brand\" style=\"cursor:pointer;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:9px 16px;border:2px solid #14110c;background:#fff;color:#14110c;box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #14110c\">BRAND</span><span class=\"wfx-chip\" data-filter=\"Murals\" style=\"cursor:pointer;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:9px 16px;border:2px solid #14110c;background:#fff;color:#14110c;box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #14110c\">MURALS</span></div>\n</section>"
      }
